snippet.title: Season 5 Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
#Overwatch2 Season 5 launches June 13! 

Embark on a mythic adventure to defeat the Demon Lord through a reimagined Battle Pass, experience Mythic Skin Progression as you unlock all three stages of Mythic Adventurer Tracer, and earn rewards in brand new ways with Questwatch! 

A new prop hunt game mode like never before in Mischief and Magic. 

Have some fun in the sun with the return of the Summer Games.

Enjoy quality-of-life updates like the return of the On Fire system.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
–
Follow #Overwatch2 for the latest news:
